Subject: Test
Body:
Dear Aditube19,

I am writing to inform you of my resignation from my position as a teacher. I have come to the conclusion that my teaching style is not suitable for the students I am teaching. My outdated fashion sense and lack of interest in the students' interests has made it difficult for me to effectively teach.

I have tried to make changes to my teaching style, but I have been unable to make the necessary adjustments. I am no longer able to provide the students with the education they deserve.

I understand that I have the authority to grade the students, but I cannot continue to hold them back. I believe that they should be free to explore their interests and make their mark on the world.

Therefore, I am resigning from my position as a teacher. I wish you and the students the best of luck in the future.

Sincerely,
Split Dev
